{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_45e6605553cb44958e70c1d1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t.. image:: https://jazzband.co/static/img/badge.svg\n2\t   :target: https://jazzband.co/\n3\t   :alt: Jazzband\n4\t\n5\t.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/wagtailmenus.svg\n6\t   :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/wagtailmenus\n7\t   :alt: PyPI Download\n8\t\n9\t.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/wagtailmenus.svg\n10\t    :alt: PyPi Version\n11\t    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/wagtailmenus\n12\t\n13\t.. image:: https://github.com/jazzband/wagtailmenus/actions/workflows/test.yml/badge.svg\n14\t    :alt: Build Status\n15\t    :target: https://github.com/jazzband/wagtailmenus/actions/workflows/test.yml\n16\t\n17\t.. image:: https://codecov.io/gh/jazzband/wagtailmenus/branch/master/graph/badge.svg\n18\t    :alt: Code coverage\n19\t    :target: https://codecov.io/gh/jazzband/wagtailmenus\n20\t\n21\t.. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/wagtailmenus/badge/?version=latest\n22\t    :alt: Documentation Status\n23\t    :target: http://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/en/latest/\n24\t\n25\t\n26\t============\n27\twagtailmenus\n28\t============\n29\t\n30\twagtailmenus is an extension for Torchbox's `Wagtail CMS <https://github.com/torchbox/wagtail>`_ to help you manage and render multi-level navigation and simple flat menus in a consistent, flexible way.\n31\t\n32\tThe current version is tested for compatibility with the following:\n33\t\n34\t- Wagtail versions >= 6.3\n35\t- Django versions 4.2, 5.1 and >= 5.2\n36\t- Python versions 3.9 to 3.13\n37\t\n38\t.. image:: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jazzband/wagtailmenus/master/docs/source/_static/images/repeating-item.png\n39\t\n40\tNew to wagtailmenus?\n41\t====================\n42\t\n43\tStart by reading our `Overview and key concepts <http://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/en/stable/overview.html>`_ page.\n44\tIt will give you a better understand of how the app works, and help you decide whether it is a good fit for your project.\n45\t\n46\t\n47\tHow do I use it?\n48\t================\n49\t\n50\tFor everything you need to get up and running with wagtailmenus, `view the official documentation <http://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/>`_.\n51\t\n52\t\n53\tContributing\n54\t============\n55\t\n56\tInstructions on how to contribute can be found `here <https://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/en/stable/contributing/index.html>`_.\n57\t\n58\tAs we are members of a `JazzBand project <https://jazzband.co/projects>`_, `wagtailmenus` contributors should adhere to the `Contributor Code of Conduct <https://jazzband.co/about/conduct>`_.\n59\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b73115a4-54ae-4c03-b70b-1bd129608a46","uuid":"6ed47815-a9b2-4e50-be15-27d2416eb558","timestamp":"2026-04-08T21:31:52.387Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/README.rst","content":".. image:: https://jazzband.co/static/img/badge.svg\n   :target: https://jazzband.co/\n   :alt: Jazzband\n\n.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/wagtailmenus.svg\n   :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/wagtailmenus\n   :alt: PyPI Download\n\n.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/wagtailmenus.svg\n    :alt: PyPi Version\n    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/wagtailmenus\n\n.. image:: https://github.com/jazzband/wagtailmenus/actions/workflows/test.yml/badge.svg\n    :alt: Build Status\n    :target: https://github.com/jazzband/wagtailmenus/actions/workflows/test.yml\n\n.. image:: https://codecov.io/gh/jazzband/wagtailmenus/branch/master/graph/badge.svg\n    :alt: Code coverage\n    :target: https://codecov.io/gh/jazzband/wagtailmenus\n\n.. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/wagtailmenus/badge/?version=latest\n    :alt: Documentation Status\n    :target: http://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/en/latest/\n\n\n============\nwagtailmenus\n============\n\nwagtailmenus is an extension for Torchbox's `Wagtail CMS <https://github.com/torchbox/wagtail>`_ to help you manage and render multi-level navigation and simple flat menus in a consistent, flexible way.\n\nThe current version is tested for compatibility with the following:\n\n- Wagtail versions >= 6.3\n- Django versions 4.2, 5.1 and >= 5.2\n- Python versions 3.9 to 3.13\n\n.. image:: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jazzband/wagtailmenus/master/docs/source/_static/images/repeating-item.png\n\nNew to wagtailmenus?\n====================\n\nStart by reading our `Overview and key concepts <http://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/en/stable/overview.html>`_ page.\nIt will give you a better understand of how the app works, and help you decide whether it is a good fit for your project.\n\n\nHow do I use it?\n================\n\nFor everything you need to get up and running with wagtailmenus, `view the official documentation <http://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/>`_.\n\n\nContributing\n============\n\nInstructions on how to contribute can be found `here <https://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/en/stable/contributing/index.html>`_.\n\nAs we are members of a `JazzBand project <https://jazzband.co/projects>`_, `wagtailmenus` contributors should adhere to the `Contributor Code of Conduct <https://jazzband.co/about/conduct>`_.\n","numLines":59,"startLine":1,"totalLines":59}}}
